<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA53">
<l>neṟiyār kuḻaṟkaṟṟai muṉṉiṉṟu piṉṟāḻn</l>
<l>taṟiyā tiḷaṅkiriyeṉ ṟeṇṇip – piriyātu</l>
<l>pūṅkoṭikkaḷ vaikum porupuṉaṟ kuṉṟeṉṉum</l>
<l>vēṅkaṭamē yāmvirumpum veṟpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vēṅkaṭam  is the mountain we long for, called a hill</l>
<l>with dashing floods where flower creepers stay without letting lose,</l>
<l>unwittingly thinking the masses of curls, that stay in front [and] hang down</l>  
<l>the backs of those of the [religious] path, are a young mountain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
